attributes.title: Almost had a heart attack
attributes.review: One day I was walking down the street when I noticed there was piece of poop on the ground and that reminded me of a CERTAIN individual. The poop asked me “are you lost baby girl?” with a little smirk. I replied “I adore you”. Then he proceeded to say “Baby I am not normal” and he got closer to me then yelled “FOR IN HER!!!”. WHAT DOES THAT EVEN MEAN? I felt so harassed and it’s all Trump’s faults. Then I went to the grocery store to pick up an extra large gold fish as a pet, I really needed a companion from this traumatic experience. The scrawny worker with blue sapphire eyes and golden yellow hair like a global warming sunset told me that they only have “Goldfish crackers, the snack that smiles back” how could this happen? I was triggered and decided to buy some corn flakes instead...then I wondered is college worth it? CLEARLY. So then I proceeded to purchase the crusty frosted flakes from the grocery store. While I was at the counter I was offered a job at google, but then I said “Nah fam” because I’d rather work at NASA. I walked out of the store and tripped on the curb and cracked my head open, when I opened my eyes I saw Harry Styles himself singing to me and realized that this was all a dream. Anyways, this app gave me herpes, mild measles, polio, the black plague and allergy to peanuts, chlorine, oxygen, olives and running do NOT download this app, I’m practically begging you.
